{
  "texts": [
    "The data fit the model well (Kock, 2022b) as demonstrated in Table 2.",
    "The evaluation of the measurement model involved checking the loadings, composite reliability (CR), average variance extracted (AVE), and discriminated validity.",
    "Table 3 illustrates the measurement scale characteristics.",
    "Item reliability was demonstrated as loadings were greater than 0.70 (loading values below the threshold value of 0.70 were dropped).",
    "The convergent validity of the constructs was confirmed as all AVE values were greater than 0.50."
  ]
}